    /// duration (e.g., `24 hours`, `1 week`, `30 days`), or an ISO 8601 duration (e.g., `PT24H`,
    /// `P7D`, `P30D`).
    ///
    /// Durations do not respect semantics of the local time zone and are always resolved to a fixed
