    /// (e.g., `2006-12-02`) resolved based on your system's configured time zone, a "friendly"
    /// duration (e.g., `24 hours`, `1 week`, `30 days`), or an ISO 8601 duration (e.g., `PT24H`,
    /// `P7D`, `P30D`).
